data.title: Plaid Cymru
data.meta_description: Plaid Cymru Plaid Cymru was founded in 1925 and won its first seat in 1966. Leanne Wood is the leader of Plaid and has been for since around 2010.
data.text:
Here a few of Plaid's policies:

- To promote the constitutional advancement of Wales with a view to reaching independence within the EU

- To ensure economic prosperity, social justice, and the health of the natural environment

- To create a bilingual society from promoting the revival of Welsh
